title: The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-Host Out of Town Guests Overnight in the Guest Suite', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-The Board Room is Perfect for Private Meetings', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Payments', 'Accepted: Credit Card, Cash via MoneyGram, Apple Pay and FREE E-Check', '-Pet Friendly Featuring Pet Spa and Bark Park', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
